ActNational Security and Intelligence Committee of Parliamentarians Act
PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE DIANE FINLEY, P.C., a member of the House of Commons who belongs to a party that is not the government party, to be a member of the National Security and Intelligence Committee of Parliamentarians, to hold office during pleasure until the dissolution of Parliament following her appointment.
